<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Resume 2</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-Evv84Mr4kqVGRNSgIGL/F/aIDqQb7xQ2vcrdIwxfjThSH8CSR7PBEakCr51Ck+w+/U6swU2Im1vVX0SVk9ABhg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />

    <style>

    :root {
  --bg-dark: #0a0a0a;             /* Overall background */
  --text-light: #ffffff;         /* Main white text */
  --accent-blue: #00d2ff;        /* Neon blue accent (lines, highlights) */
  --text-muted: #bbbbbb;         /* Sub text or secondary info */
  --card-bg: #121212;            /* Section box background */
  --skill-bg: #1e1e1e;           /* Skill icon background */
  --skill-border: #00bfff;       /* Skill icon border */
}


    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: var(--text-light);
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    }

    main{
        height: 100vh;
        width: 100%;
        padding-top: 3%;
        background-color: #eff6e0;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .resume{
        height:90%;
        width: 35%;
        background-color: var(--bg-dark);
        padding: 2%;
        border-radius: 2rem;
    }

@media print {
  .resume {
    width: 210mm;
    min-height: 297mm;
    padding: 20mm;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    border-radius: 0;
    background: white;
    color: black;
  }

  body, html, main {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background: white;
  }

  #down {
    display: none; /* hide download button in PDF */
  }
}


    
    .nav{
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        border-bottom: 3px solid var(--skill-border);
        padding-bottom:3%;
    }

    .nav h2{
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 2.3rem;
    }
    .nav h4{
        font-weight: 200;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom:0.5rem;
        color: var(--accent-blue);
    }
    .img{
        height: 130px;
        width: 130px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        border: 2px solid var(--skill-border);
        box-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--accent-blue), 0 0 5px var(--accent-blue), 0 0 5px var(--accent-blue);
    }

    .nav p{
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .nav i{
        color: var(--accent-blue);
    }

    section{
        padding: 5% 0;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        border-bottom: 2px solid var(--skill-border);
        color: var(--text-light);
    }

    .summary{
        width: 50%;
        height: 160px;
        border-right: 2px solid var(--skill-border);
    }

    .summary p{
        font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
     .skill{
        width: 50%;
        height: 160px;
        border-left: 2px solid var(--skill-border);
        padding-left: 1rem;
    }

    section p{
        margin-top:0.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    section p i{
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: var(--accent-blue);
        margin-right: 0.5rem;
    }
   
#sum{
    border: none;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--skill-border);
    padding: none;
    padding-left: 1rem;
}

#skill{
    border: none;
    border-right: 2px solid var(--skill-border);
    padding-left: 0rem;
}

#down{
    height: 3rem;
    width: 8rem;
    border: none;
    outline: none;
    color: var(--text-light);
    background-color: var(--bg-dark);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--skill-border);
    border-radius: 2rem;
    transition: 0.4s ease;
}

#down:hover{
    color: var(--bg-dark);
    background-color:var(--text-light) ;
    border: 2px solid var(--skill-border);
}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main>
        <div class="resume">
           <div class="nav">
            <div class="img"></div>
            <div class="text">
                <h2>&nbsp;<%= data.name %></h2>
                <h4>&nbsp;<%= data.skills %></h4>
                <p><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i>&nbsp; <%= data.email %> &nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp; <i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i>&nbsp;<%= data.phone %> <br><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<%= data.adress %></p>
            </div>
           </div>

           <section>
            <div class="summary">
                <h3>Summary</h3>
               <p>
  I am a passionate and driven individual based in <%= data.adress %>. I hold a degree in <%= data.degree %> from <%= data.collage %> College with a CGPA of <%= data.CGPA %>. With <%= data.experience %>years of hands-on experience, I have developed strong skills in <%= data.skills %>. I am committed to applying my knowledge in challenging environments and continuously growing as a professional.
</p>

            </div>
            <div class="skill">
                <h3>Education & degree</h3>
                <p><i class="fa-solid fa-user-graduate"></i><%= data.degree %></p>
                <h3>Collage & final year</h3>
                <p><i class="fa-solid fa-school-flag"></i><%= data.collage %> in <%= data.passyear %></p>
                <h3>CGPA</h3>
                <p><i class="fa-solid fa-award"></i><%= data.CGPA %></p>
            </div>
           </section>


           
           <section>
            <div class="skill" id="skill">
                <h3>Skills</h3>
                <p><i class="fa-solid fa-laptop-code"></i><%= data.skills %></p>
                <h3>Project</h3>
                <p><i class="fa-solid fa-code-fork"></i><%= data.project %></p>
            </div>

            <div id="sum" class="summary">
                <h3>About Your Project</h3>
               <p>My project is about those hcakers who can't able to pay charges to paid racon tools so my tool is abosulutely free so eithical can use for thrir profit while bug bounty</p>
            </div>
           </section>
        </div>

        <button id="down" onclick="downloadPDF()">Download</button>
    </main>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/html2pdf.js/0.10.1/html2pdf.bundle.min.js"></script>
<script>
